data.description: Own this beautiful spacious 4 bedroom home in Carriage Hills.   As you walk through the front door on your left you have the formal living and dining room (with a door that leads to the kitchen) - perfect to greet your guests. And the bedrooms are to your right.  There are 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The main bedroom is a suite complete with its own bathroom. As you continue past the foyer you will enter the cozy den and to the left is the eat-in kitchen area, as well, as the kitchen.  Off the kitchen is a laundry room large enough for storage, too. There is a NEW stove in kitchen and NEW carpet in den.  For outdoor entertainment, there is a large covered bricked patio. The yard is spacious and there is a storage building that's perfect to store lawn equipment.  Give me a call so I can show you this home before it’s gone!
